reviewText: I had this movie on VHS and was looking for it on dvd for a long time. It's one of my favorites. It's a beautiful movie about the daughter of a gangster who is claimed to do miracles. It's a great movie that will leave you feeling good.

Nice change of pace for R.J. and a story that really reflects what the Church does and has done dealing with possible sainthood for someone.

Jazzman65
